private boolean isLiteral(char c) throws IOException {
switch (c) {
case '/':
case '\\':
case ';':
case '#':
case '=':
checkLenient(); // fall-through
case '{':
case '}':
case '[':
case ']':
case ':':
case ',':
case ' ':
case '\t':
case '\f':
case '\r':
case '\n':
return false;
default:
return true;
}
}
